{"tid":28381,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"每次係Harrods.com買野都一肚火","createTime":"2016-12-08T01:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T12:52:40.000Z","uid":37389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8839519b8587d5ecc825313bd66285660abc91d2","tid":28381,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:58:01.000Z","msg":"因為佢直送香港又有退稅所以之前都有係佢到買衫, 屌次次比錢時唔係直接出error with your payment 就係hang左係度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴晚我見佢7折又買下野咁, 用dbs同hsbc visa master 試齊都係error, 焗我用最貴嘅amex <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原本以為得左啦終於收到confirmation, 點知瞓醒見到另一個email 話 problem with payment 叫我打比amex. 打完過去銀行話本黎已經過左數, 係harrods自己一個鐘後主動call back <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌.... 到底係我呢個客真係咁可疑定係harrods廢... <br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲都有咁嘅經歷?"},{"pid":"d39a182b05c624dc43066387490bb32dafc2e4e7","tid":28381,"uid":20528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"個網都死撚埋 琴日都上到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78dd172237fa3d317d5d849f52cc0d19c3e95a20","tid":28381,"uid":22484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:29:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個網都死撚埋 琴日都上到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n9折都死.. 7折好難唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f9eaa53d4129a2b54dfbeab87974b403d48758","tid":28381,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:07:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個網都死撚埋 琴日都上到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家上到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實最怪係香港時間朝早上唔到但英國時間上到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3401b258f12d74efc4aa19c914d29d1346d807f1","tid":28381,"uid":37389,"like